# .null Portal — environment
#
# Optional: override the public Solana RPC. Defaults to mainnet-beta public RPC.
# For production use a paid endpoint (Helius/Triton/QuickNode) to avoid the
# public RPC's rate limits on getProgramAccounts (the "My Names" scan).
#
# NOTE: this is a PUBLIC (NEXT_PUBLIC_) var — it ships in the browser bundle.
# Never put a secret API key here that you don't want exposed. If your provider
# needs a key, front it with a proxy and point this at the proxy URL.
NEXT_PUBLIC_RPC_URL=https://api.mainnet-beta.solana.com
